      :
      <b>
       sprtn pzz npltn
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       A gd Npltn pzz s  thng f sprtn bty: mnml ngrdnts tht r frsh, stnd t, nd cm tgthr n  wy tht trnscnds fd nd rt nd bty — t’s n ct f pr lv.
      </p>
      <p>
       My fvrt s th Mrghrt. A smpl crst s hnd-md, hnd-strtchd, sprd thnly wth frsh tmt sc, wth chnks f mzzrll (r vgn chs) nd sprgs f bsl strwn bt ts srfc, fnshd ff wth  drzzl f prfct lv l. It gs nt n ncrdbly ht wd vn, whr th crst blstrs n 60 scnds nd, n tht brfst mmnt f prty by fr,  mrcl ccrs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th mrcl s tht ths smpl ngrdnts — flr, wtr, tmts, chs, bsl, l, slt — bcm th mst hvnly sbstnc n th nvrs: lv.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ech ngrdnt, bcs t’s nt vrwhlmd by  smrgsbrd f tppngs (ssgs nd fr knds f chs nd crmlzd nns nd Th chckn nd brccl r wht hv y), cn b tstd dstnctly nd pprctd fr ts smpl bty. Hvng fwr ngrdnts llws ch t ssrt tslf.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt thy ls cm tgthr n n ct f prfct nty, nd ths shws wht mnmlsm s bt. A fw thngs f bty, whn strppd f th xtrns, r llwd t brth, t shn, t thn crt  whl tht s bttr thn  whl f t mny lss mprtnt thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ths s tr f pzz, bt ls f wrk nd lf. Ct bck t  fw mprtnt tsks nd yr wrk wll b trnsfrmd. D nly  fw thngs n lf nd ths thngs wll brth nd tk n n mprtnc thy nvr hd bfr. Thy wll crt  lf tht s nt nly bttr bt s  trr xprssn f yrslf nt pssbl wtht mnmlsm.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mnmlsm llws yr lf t b n ct f lv.
      </p>
